    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_000</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おかえり、兄ちゃん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Welcome home, brother! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>腹へった〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm hungryyyy... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この人たち、誰〜？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, who are these people? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お客さんだ。静かにしてろよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They're guests so behave yourselves. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この子たちは？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who are these kids? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争で親を亡くした子どもたちだ。
オレが引き取って面倒みてる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These kids lost their parents in the war... So I decided to 
take care of them myself. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ミリー、お客さんが来たときは
どうするんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milly, how do we greet our guests? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お茶〜！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With tea! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>腹へったよ〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm still hungryyy... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>グリッド、ジョンに
飯の支度を
してやってくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Grid, prepare John some food. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>火使ってもいいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it okay to use fire? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、オレもいるしな。
なにかあったら呼ぶんだぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. I'll be around here. If anything happens just gimme a 
shout. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さてと。なんだっけ、&lt;Cless&gt;と
&lt;Mint&gt;に会いに来たんだったか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With that out of the way... Why was it you came here to 
meet with &lt;Cless&gt; and &lt;Mint&gt;? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266344</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん、えっと……
何から話せばいいかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, huh... Where should we start from? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なるほど……
マクスウェルってことは、
&lt;Red&gt;モーリア坑道&lt;White&gt;だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's that... To meet Maxwell you'll need to go to the 
Morlia Mineshaft. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、オレが一緒に
行ってやるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's decided, I'll go with you guys. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269324</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも&lt;Chester&gt;さんも
忙しいんじゃねーの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, isn't Mister &lt;Chester&gt; busy? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ああ、オレは
&lt;Cless&gt;や&lt;Mint&gt;とは
違うんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Nah. I'm not &lt;Cless&gt; or &lt;Mint&gt;, you know. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと言い方がキツいせいで
周りから『コワいヤツ』って
思われてるみたいだしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe I'm trying too hard to pull the tough act. It's all 
thanks that someone told me I was "too weak" a long time ago. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_025</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもさ、
あの子どもたちには
したわれてんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, can you really leave these kids behind? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_026</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、子どもにはな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kids? Hah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃ、行くかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right, let's get moving. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_028</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>兄ちゃん！　どこ行くんだ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Big brother! Are you going somewhere!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_029</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、ちょっとそこまでな。
おとなしく留守番してろよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yup, I'll be out for a bit. You guys take care of 
everything here, okay? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_030</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>置いてっちゃやだ〜！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't leaaave us! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_031</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>腹へった〜！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm STILL hungry! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_032</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すぐ帰ってくるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll return soon! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_033</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ジョン、食いすぎて腹壊すなよ。
ミリー、寝る前には歯磨きだぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>John, don't eat so much or you'll get stomach ache! Milly, 
brush your teeth before going to bed! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_034</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>グリッド、
ふたりのこと頼んだぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Grid, I leave these two on your care. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_035</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う、うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-yeah... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_036</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さ、行くぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, let's get moving! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_037</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>い、いいんですか、
&lt;Chester&gt;さん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A-are you sure about this, Mister &lt;Chester&gt;? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_038</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、道場の連中も親切で、
面倒見てくれてるからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sure. The Dojo's trainees will also take care of things 
here. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_039</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それから、
『さん』はいらないぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, and drop the whole "Mister" thing. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_040</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　マジか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>R-really? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_041</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もちろんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_110_070_042</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかった！　よろしくな、
&lt;Chester&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, then! Nice to have you around, &lt;Chester&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
